data.title: 50 states, 50 spots: Natural wonders
data.meta_description: You don't have to go far to find natural beauty in the United States. From colossal canyons to sky-scraping peaks, towering redwoods to shimmering rivers, there are must-see wonders in every state.
data.text: Purple mountain majesties. Fruited plains. Oceans white with foam. Thereâs a reason songwriters wax poetic about Americaâs abundance of natural beauty. At least 50 reasons, actually. As the United States goes on vacation, CNN is showcasing a natural wonder in each of the 50 states. Some are world-renowned and undeniably spectacular, while others are less-discovered gems.
